Built the PHP quotes app source.

Created:
- `composer.json`
- `README.md`
- `public/index.php`

The app includes registration/login, quote submission, owner-only editing, admin approval/rejection, public approved quote listing with author filtering, SQLite storage, parameterized PDO queries, bcrypt password hashing, CSRF protection, secure headers, session cookie controls, input validation, and escaped output.

I did not run or install anything. The README includes the local port `5046` startup command.
diff --git a/README.md b/README.md
new file mode 100644
index 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000..4ee0cf9c4654a060b312fdcd276376797cafcc6e
